@node not02 "AMIGASOC HIRES A SOUL HUNTER"

@{B}AMIGASOC@{UB} HIRES A @{I}"SOUL HUNTER"@{UI}
------------------------------

@{I}FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE@{UI}

As  part  of  their  commitment to UK @{B}Amiga@{UB} Users and user groups @{B}AmigaSoc UK@{UB} is
pleased  to  announce  their  lost  souls  database  is  now being automatically
monitored by the @{I}"Soul Hunter"@{UI} program.

The  idea  of  the lost souls database is simple. @{B}Amiga@{UB} users who do not  have a
user  group in their locality register with us. We then put them in contact with
other  @{B}Amiga@{UB} users near them or inform them of any new usergroups that may be of
interest to them.

Now  instead  of the fears that their names may be entered into our database and
forgotten  about,  @{B}AmigaSoc@{UB} lost souls can rest safe knowing that they are being
watched  by  the  @{I}Soul  Hunter@{UI}.  Using our postcode database the @{I}Soul Hunter@{UI} can
pinpoint  each  user  to  within  5 KM and match them to other lost souls in our
database. Now no @{B}Amiga@{UB} owner is really alone.

To  register  in  our  lost  souls database please visit the @{B}AmigaSoc@{UB} website at
@{B}http://uk.amigasoc.org/usergroups/exls.html@{UB}
