@node not05 "THE INFORMER ISSUE 16 IS NOW AVAILABLE"

@{B}THE INFORMER ISSUE 16@{UB} IS NOW AVAILABLE
--------------------------------------

@{I}FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE@{UI}

Greetings all,

Issue  16  of  @{B}The Amiga Informer@{UB} is now available at all our retail dealers. To
