announced  @{B}OS  3.5@{UB}  upgrade  and  what  you  can  expect from it. We also take a
critical  look  at  the work that needs to be done by @{B}Amiga Inc.@{UB} to get the ball
rolling  again.  In  addition  to  other  recent news and our usual columns like
@{B}Workbench  Enhancements@{UB},  @{B}Caught  in  the AmiNet@{UB}, and @{B}Audio Adventures@{UB}, issue 16
brings  you  a  truck load of product reviews. This issue evaluates 13 products,
including;  @{B}Wildfire@{UB}, @{B}EZ-VGA@{UB} scandoubler/flicker-fixer, @{B}WebFTP@{UB}, @{B}Picasso 4@{UB} review
